Muscled my way through many years of emotional shit. Showed up for work. Paid my bills. Hit the gym. Helped others. Did what I thought was best but maybe it wasn't best for me. 

Too many without means to just 'check out' when in that funk. That #depression needs some rest.

It took me 3 weeks to reach out to a man whose job is working with #men with #depression. Reaching out can be incredibly challenging...and it is INCREDIBLY important. Reaching out is not weakness...it takes a great deal of strength. Reach out now to someone you trust.
